Summary for an evoverse dataset.

Source: R/S3_methods_print.R
summary.mbst_data.Rd

The summary reports basic statistics on the stored input values concerning both mutations, segments, and fits if available

# S3 method for mbst_data
summary(x, ...)

Arguments

x

An evoverse object.
...

S3 parameters

Value

Nothing.

Examples

data('example_evoverse')
summary(example_evoverse)
